welcome_message_body: Welcome to Woodinville, a charming city known for its beautiful scenery, award-winning wineries, and warm hospitality. We invite you to explore and experience all that our city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Snohomish County - Paine Field Airport serves all commercial flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the free WiFi network by selecting 'Paine Field Free WiFi' from their device's network options.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Kenmore Air Harbor SPB Airport offers check-in and boarding for all flights.

terminals.name: Water Terminal
terminals.description: The water terminal at Kenmore Air Harbor SPB Airport is used for seaplane departures and arrivals.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport houses most of the airport's amenities and services, including check-in counters, baggage claim, and security checkpoints.

terminals.name: North Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The North Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport is primarily used for Alaska Airlines and its partners, and features a variety of dining and shopping options.

terminals.name: South Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The South Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves as a hub for international flights and offers a range of duty-free shops and restaurants.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport is home to airlines such as Delta and Southwest, as well as several lounges and a variety of dining options.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves as a hub for United Airlines and its partners, and offers a variety of shops and restaurants for travelers.

terminals.name: Concourse C
terminals.description: Concourse C at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport is primarily used by American Airlines and its partners, and features a variety of amenities including a children's play area and a spa.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport, but a premium option is also offered for faster speeds.
